Mix wafer crumbs and butter; press onto bottom of 13 x 9-inch pan. Beat cream cheese, sugar and 1/4 cup milk with mixer until well blended. Stir in 1 cup COOL WHIP; spread over crust. Beat pudding mixes and remaining milk with whisk 2 min. Stir in 1/4 cup caramel topping. Spoon over cream cheese layer; top with remaining COOL WHIP. Refrigerate 5 hours or until firm. Top with apples, nuts and remaining caramel topping just before serving.